lead_paragraph: Reserve Allen Crabbe scored 21 points and the Portland Trail Blazers cruised to a 105-93 victory over the short-handed Sacramento Kings on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Crabbe Has 21 and Blazers Beat Kings 105-93
